The Fugitive Season 1 (1963)
S01E08 See Hollywood and Die

First aired: 11/5/1963 
While working as a gas station attendant in New Mexico, Kimble is taken hostage, along with customer Joanne, by two holdup men, named Miles and Vinnie. Once on the road, Kimble pretends that he is a criminal and is heading towards Los Angels for a "big job." At the same time, he lets Joanne know that he&#039;s on her side, but she&#039;s suspicious to his true motives. Once arriving in L.A., Kimble decides to set up Miles and Vinnie to be arrested. But Miles, not trusting Kimble enough, wants him to kill Joanne to prove himself. J. Pat O&#039;Malley, Brenda Vaccaro guest star.
